node.text: The Tasty dining room proudly presents a pizza that will have you feeling like the guest of honor. To make this fairytale-inspired pizza, cut a loaf of French bread in half and top it with a French onion soup-inspired sauce, Fontina and Gruyére cheeses, and caramelized onions. Then, shape an edible enchanted rose out of salami and parsley to give this dish the happily-ever-after it deserves. Link in bio for the recipe 🌹

node.text: These tacos were inspired by a popular Hawaiian dish called loco moco, which features a bed or rice topped with a beef patty, gravy, and an over-easy egg. In our version, we deep fry a mixture of rice and flour into crispy taco shells and fill them with deliciously tender braised short ribs, a fried egg, and flavorful gravy made from the short rib braising! 🌮  Link in bio 😋
